{"tid":785721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"759 老細死左","createTime":"2018-08-19T12:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T12:37:34.000Z","uid":183971,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"83a4a03dc522cdb677ffbc030ad7313493567b7a","tid":785721,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:19:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180819/58583418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F58583418&d=q6sYCdTlnVntpQwkAG5Zb8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=71056efd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F58583418&h=067490bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180819/58583418</a><br />\n<br />\nCEC國際控股（759）有限公司發公告表示，759阿信屋創辦人兼主席林偉駿昨日於在養和醫院逝世。<br />\n<br />\n公司董事會將盡力按已故主席訂立的策略繼續經營集團之業務。將重組其架構，並適時刊發進一步公告。<br />\n<br />\n公告未有透露其逝世原因。"},{"pid":"7058aab198663efed9bcdad8165ea1b1fe68f3b9","tid":785721,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:35:24.000Z","msg":"【事出突然】759阿信屋老闆林偉駿逝世　<br />\n【事出突然】759阿信屋老闆林偉駿逝世<br />\n<br />\nCEC國際控股（759）有限公司發公告表示，759阿信屋創辦人兼主席林偉駿昨日於在養和醫院逝世。<br />\n<br />\n公司董事會將盡力按已故主席訂立的策略繼續經營集團之業務。將重組其架構，並適時刊發進一步公告。公告未有透露其逝世原因。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者今年6月1日下午曾於養和醫院內分泌及糖尿病中心碰見林偉駿，當時他身穿便服，站在接待處前等候。養和醫院網站資料顯示，該中心專為糖尿及內分泌疾病患者提供一站式治療及護理服務，駐場醫護包括糖尿病專科醫生，還有糖尿病專科護士和足病診療師等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180819&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58583418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180819%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58583418&d=q6sYCdTlnVntpQwkAG5Zb8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e656b13d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180819%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58583418&h=e0e7ff00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180819&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58583418</a><br />\n<br />\nsent by HK News 香港新聞報紙:<a href=\"http://goo.gl/Vn18QN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FVn18QN&d=q6sYCdTlnVntpQwkAG5Zb8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=2acee75c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goo.gl/Vn18QN</a>"},{"pid":"9e1879b604afe5e2a7398444e97db1ec0c7ac6d1","tid":785721,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"rip"}]}